    "headline": "Faster decisions, faster care for patients: Cognizant opens TriZetto Unify to AI agents",
    "summary": "Cognizant (NASDAQ: CTSH) is putting AI agents to work on one of U.S. healthcare's most persistent administrative bottlenecks: prior authorization. A new headless API model treats AI agents as first-tier consumers of TriZetto Unify, Cognizant's platform strategy that spans payer and provider workflows. Electronic Prior Authorization is the first solution to go live, following the rollout of TriZetto Assistant and TriZetto Autonomous Workflow Agents to existing customers.",
